{"tid":831480,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[我要登上潮文界嘅寶座] HONG KONG NO IT #勸世文 #獅子山精神  #創科導航 #如有類同，實屬巧合","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T05:14:29.000Z","uid":125976,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f97d1b5fe1c91342efc2f37e8d6b6864dac48379","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"你好，我叫小強，今年三十歲，係一名香港資深軟件工程師。乜撚嘢軟件工程師呀，IT 狗就 IT 狗啦，點叫都係撚狗一名啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n漏咗「是咁的」？是鳩但啦，加咗會發達㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔差在啦，都得返半條人命囉，成為潮文以警後人都唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家做 in-house 都係間中俾人撚吓，執吓十年前嘅爛 code 炒吓股咁，又唔洗點 OT，算係執到身彩啦。<br />\n<br />\n我朋友禿頭明做 vendor 做到隻屄咁，叫乜 full stack developer 喎，每日未做到八九點都唔洗走，人工先得萬尾，依咪叫 code 盡人亡囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得以前真係好有心機學電腦㗎，小六由 Flash 開始學起，已經識整吓網頁仔玩吓改 M$ Windows 登錄檔，初中仲整咗隻 Flash Game 攞過吓獎添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然冇呀局長咁見識甚廣親眼見過 Steve Jobs，但都好仰慕佢㗎，成日幻想自己會唔會係下一個 Steve Jobs, Mark Zuckerberg。<br />\n<br />\n我咁諗，做唔到 Steve Jobs 都好，都入到 Google, Facebook 掛。佢哋個 Office 咁靚，大個仔一定要入去見識吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家諗返，自問冇父幹又唔係真係最聰明嗰批，做 Steve Jobs 點輪到你，幫到楷哥挽鞋底算偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年好記得我同呀大頭文一齊「搞機」，搞彎晒學校啲電腦，幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其實當年我同大頭文都喺公開試考差唔多分，但當時我有埋土 Offer，佢冇，佢仲好唔開心添。但最後佢過咗美國，入到間 banding 更好嘅 U，仲入埋 Facebook 添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家唔開心嗰個係我，人又老、胃又痛、錢又冇、女又溝唔到，每日好似 take 嘢咁 take 抗抑鬱藥同胃藥，得返半條人命。所以窮人真係唔好生仔，因果業報好重㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得讀梗 U 嘅時期小朋友唔識世界，自己接過吓大大少少嘅 Projects 嚟做，剩計畀人走數嗰度都分分鐘有十萬八萬。香港啲 SME 最鐘意走 IT 狗數㗎啦，毒撚一條叫你做又唔識 say no，做完就可以駛走你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣啲 professor 仲問我點解咁勁 Year 1 就識 Ajax 同幫人起網購。大佬呀，窮命一條唔洗搵食咩，到最後當然錢都賺唔到幾多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一畢業當然雄心壯志，諗住搞吓 product 啦，見人哋整磁能線、咖啡機、機頂盒都攞到 funding，冇理由唔試一試掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知用啲窮撚半鹹半淡嘅英文寫撚咗份 business plan，個 fund man 同我講：「你返鄉下耕田啦，你以為就咁就會俾 funding 你，你家底又冇人脈又冇，邊個擔保你唔會攞咗筆錢走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n所以話呢後生仔，香港搞 IT 最梗要有家底同吹得兩嘴英文，如果唔係你識 React, Flutter, Docker, Serverless 都係食得屎㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇吓洗米華個仔，唔通人哋又識揼 code 咩，人哋就係勝在有家底，請你哋班狗去寫，最後咪成功「旋轉」囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港始終唔係矽谷，冇人會因為你揼 code 揼得幾勁而拍手掌。<br />\n<br />\n後生仔唔好發夢啦，乖乖哋畀心機爬上「不公平線」之上，做醫生、律師、ibanker 好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 我投胎去矽谷先，你哋慢慢發你哋個大灣區夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df830dd31a5cb902ef5f6e2c3ebc876994bd6cb","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/115259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F115259_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=603c4489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38eb1b326e8dcfc19866c4c96c597527cf5b2b1b","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"sh\">git push origin master --force</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7ebc8ebdb2af153ed256c6a2fcc3076ff93dfff1","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/120502_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F120502_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5693caf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推吓 SEO 先"},{"pid":"6d7a3d5a64ea0d5a928b9c57dc8618c47b82223b","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"如果有一千個 like 轉埋英文寫上 Medium<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430d7494f3715375951501788d6910b40c831e66","tid":831480,"uid":114518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"潮文就算唔上<br />\n但你咁比心機寫 點都支持下<br />\n我自己都識唔少IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6055c37583fa19b83b779fe2f62781f61c4b723c","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430d7494f3715375951501788d6910b40c831e66","tid":831480,"uid":114518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"潮文就算唔上<br />\n但你咁比心機寫 點都支持下<br />\n我自己都識唔少IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"點先可以登上潮文界嘅雅座呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我轉行做寫文乞吓食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e66330236e9ea0776e0df5f227691fb04640ee2","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f32d53d67e195ea1627e180662e0fcf7c5ed50","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/123804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F123804_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e0287d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYeoman<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39082a1a9d10a4bf58656720fd9dede7268858a8","tid":831480,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b9540caae9a5e3cf78457c48602c2ac06f98ff","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39082a1a9d10a4bf58656720fd9dede7268858a8","tid":831480,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"但政府工好撚悶，聽啲朋友講嘅公作內容，明明寫個 program 就可以自動做到晒嘅嘢，都要日日人手做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然香港 IT 都好撚悶"},{"pid":"394c151fa95fdc3dfcc57ddccb63740e04e04b0b","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/124423_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F124423_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cbae1b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭 J 圖，大家一齊推動香港創科</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c9aa2d5c5605501b660f58d72289f8051e9cc033","tid":831480,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"寵物店都無得賣IT狗.."},{"pid":"c384310baaf79d70081515d73e9ff92c5c78b1e7","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9aa2d5c5605501b660f58d72289f8051e9c