wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c197d7915bc13732201cc15d3c502de357bb0ff7","tid":831480,"uid":121636,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過 openball？香港產品，個創辦人專登走去矽谷坐足半年建立 network，而家喺美國做得好好<br />\n<br />\n有冇聽過 editgrid？最近蘋果發布會果個人，十幾年前已經做掂比蘋果收購<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多香港嘅 GIS 公司，其實蘋果喺四五前搞 Apple Map 時都頻頻收購<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打真係有料，喺香港絕對可以搵到食，機會總是有的。<br />\n<br />\n我有個 VC 朋友同我講<br />\n<br />\n「如果你要百幾二百萬呢，就唔好搵我喇。你黎 pitch 我，講到你對自己咁有信心、咁有料、咁睇好前景，咁不如你自己儲，自己借，點都會 R 到百幾萬返黎，我唔貪你果 5-10% 股份。等你需要搵人投資一千萬以上，真正要將生意擴大到壟斷，你自己都冇辦法到籌到咁多，再黎搵我喇！」"},{"pid":"26e99118560326f246e4c832afcacb536d829ec0","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b19543ac2d603934a02ed66dc57380ee0edcfe","tid":831480,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72537add3997cd3ba42ed8720772ab5978a998e0","tid":831480,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1364c29272e725b1e3b2f7c20df6e0b51f21dc17","tid":831480,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"直接報外國工去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正你有料到唔信外國無人欣賞你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"indeed 度搵？<br />\n㩒過 apply 掣佢問我有冇 visa，冇係咪唔理我㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連 BNO 都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"自己試左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心小弟今年25都乜柒skill都唔識宜家學緊寫app<br />\n希望可以入到行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2